sc":"冥魂大帝倒下后，他飞散的冥魂会重组，使他复活。死亡时附近900范围内的敌人会被减速。\r\n\r\n可用神杖升级。","dmg":"","notes":"如果魔法不足冥魂大帝将不会重生。<br />如果冥魂大帝拥有不朽之守护，同时重生不处于冷却状态，死亡后将首先触发重生。<br />重生后生命值和魔法值全满。<br />对于死亡被延缓的友军，其成为冥魂前所受的最后一击来源即为击杀者。<br />冥魂重生不会影响工程师的技能自杀攻击！。<br />冥魂续命效果能作用于冥魂大帝实际的死亡，如果符合重生的条件本效果不会生效。","attrib":"重生时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">3 / 3 / 3</span><br />\n移动速度减缓： <span class=\"attribVal\">75%</span><br />\n攻击速度降低： <span class=\"attribVal\">75</span><br />\n减速持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">5</span><br />\n神杖升级冥魂续命持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">5</span><br />\n<span class=\"scepterVal\"><font color=\"#6fe771\">神杖升级冥魂续命作用范围：</font></span> <span class=\"attribVal\">1200</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:160<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:260/160/60","lore":"冥魂大帝的对头们一直很疑惑，为什么他就是不会死透。","hurl":"Wraith_King"}],"itembuilds":{"Starting":["tango","flask","clarity","branches","branches","quelling_blade"],"Early":["magic_stick","boots","helm_of_iron_will"],"Core":["magic_wand","power_treads","armlet","tpscroll"],"Luxury":["desolator","black_king_bar","assault","abyssal_blade","blink","heart","heavens_halberd","monkey_king_bar","rapier","ultimate_scepter","moon_shard"]},"skillup":[{"groupName":"常规加点","desc":"常规加点，这样的骷髅前期参展能力比较强，可以配合队友GANK。","abilityKeys":["skeleton_king_hellfire_blast","attribute_bonus","skeleton_king_hellfire_blast","attribute_bonus","skeleton_king_hellfire_blast","skeleton_king_reincarnation","skeleton_king_hellfire_blast","skeleton_king_vampiric_aura","skeleton_king_vampiric_aura","skeleton_king_mortal_strike","skeleton_king_reincarnation","skeleton_king_mortal_strike","skeleton_king_mortal_strike","skeleton_king_mortal_strike","skeleton_king_vampiric_aura","skeleton_king_reincarnation","skeleton_king_vampiric_aura","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus"]},{"groupName":"主致命加点","desc":"其实主要是前12级的加点，后面可以选择加吸血或锤子都可以；如果队友控制或者AOE能力不错的话，这样的加点在中期能打出更